                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">For partnership and collaboration inquiries.</p>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Email</p>
                        <a href="mailto:collaborate@pehlione.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            collaborate@pehlione.com
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Phone</p>
                        <a href="tel:+1555905 2345" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            +1 (555) 905-2345
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Press -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8l-4-4H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-3l-4 4z"></path>
                        </svg>
                        Press
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">For media and press inquiries.</p>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Email</p>
                        <a href="mailto:press@pehlione.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            press@pehlione.com
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Phone</p>
                        <a href="tel:+1555905 3456" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            +1 (555) 905-3456
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Join Our Team -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z"></path>
                        </svg>
                        Join Our Team
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Interested in working with us?</p>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Email</p>
                        <a href="mailto:careers@pehlione.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            careers@pehlione.com
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Phone</p>
                        <a href="tel:+1555905 4567" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            +1 (555) 905-4567
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Say Hello -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 10l-2 1m0 0l-2-1m2 1v2.5M20 7l-2 1m0 0l-2-1m2 1v2.5M14 4l-2 1m0 0L10 4m2 1v2.5M3 7l2 1m0 0l2-1m-2 1v2.5M3 7l2 1m0 0l2-1m-2 1v2.5M3 7l2 1m0 0l2-1m-2 1v2.5M3 7l2 1m0 0l2-1m-2 1v2.5M3 7l2 1m0 0l2-1m-2 1v2.5M3 7l2 1m0 0l2-1m-2 1v2.5"></path>
                        </svg>
                        Say Hello
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">General inquiries and feedback.</p>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Email</p>
                        <a href="mailto:hello@pehlione.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            hello@pehlione.com
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Phone</p>
                        <a href="tel:+1555905 5678" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">
                            +1 (555) 905-5678
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Locations Section -->
    <section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                    Our Locations
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
                    Visit us at any of our offices around the world.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
                <!-- Los Angeles -->
                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
